name: "User Abuser Boy" E-girl Poem by Sunny Crittenden
description: A poem I wrote in 1998 dedicated to the sperm donor of my 1st child who was a fucked up, smarmy, untrustworthy piece of shit I was glad to be rid of at the time. This poem is featured on my original Angelfire site at: https://www.angelfire.com/sd/lilsunny/Poetry.html
